 1994-15521994-09-130,  ,  CAN PORTS,  TC,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAmendments to the PRINCE RUPERT HARBOUR DUES BY-LAW which clarify the meaning of a number of provisions of the By-law and repeal paragraphs 7(e) and (f) which made provision under specific circumstances for exempting vessels entering the harbour from the payment of harbour dues.
